name: Working Remotely
description: Over the years, HeyTVM has been publishing animated gifs and videos that promote positivity and new perspectives on various topics. Sooo many of them include my “Bones” character. This is your chance to own some of these bonetastic animations in NFT form. Once you secure your NFB, it will take 206 minutes to reveal which NFB you now own. There are several color variations of the same animation, but also several pieces that are as rare and priceless as the bones in your body. This series includes 10K randomly generated NFTs that rest in peace on the Ethereum Blockchain.
